51:02.000 --> 51:05.000
batch of non-alcoholic wine under the same trademark,

51:05.000 --> 51:08.000
which was not prohibited to advertise.

51:08.000 --> 51:11.000
Nevertheless, the brand was heard and constantly

51:11.000 --> 51:14.000
associated with our customers with one or another product.

51:14.000 --> 51:17.000
And when they came to the store,

51:17.000 --> 51:20.000
of course, the customers recognized the brand,

51:20.000 --> 51:23.000
but they bought, most often, not non-alcoholic wine,

51:23.000 --> 51:26.000
but, of course, ordinary wine of the same trademark.

51:26.000 --> 51:29.000
Thus, such a method will help you

51:29.000 --> 51:32.000
